{"tid":1280500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(昏睡百年)  散打冠軍被「點穴大師」K.O","createTime":"2019-07-03T04:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T10:47:40.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fb9b76fbd3fb7d8ce9f714633d0dc90ec133feba","tid":1280500,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:00:19.000Z","msg":"福建省清流縣上月28日舉辦了一場武林龍鬥士中外拳王爭霸賽，武師霍燕山用點穴將「散打冠軍」齊衛華打倒。整場比賽霍燕山僅用兩回合將對方「K.O」，齊衛華倒地後渾身抽搐，難以站立。該比賽片段傳出後引發網民熱議，多位武術專家質疑該比賽造假，網民甚至懷疑齊衛華涉嫌配合表演，而今日有廈門散打權威人士稱，查無「齊衛華」此人，但霍燕山和主辦方縣文旅局人員均稱比賽真實無造假，霍燕山甚至表示接受各方挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n從片段所見，霍燕山趁齊衛華再次出腳但踢空之際，用戴上拳套的左手「點」中其左肩。齊衛華隨即倒地，狀甚痛苦。據了解，霍燕山是清流縣當地的武術協會會長，是「霍家點穴」的傳人及「太極宗師」陳小旺的弟子，今次是首次參加職業比賽；而齊衛華則據稱是廈門頗有名氣的「散打冠軍」。<br />\n<br />\n主辦單位強調：「絕對是真的，我們眼看着打到了，命中的聲音很響，現場觀眾沒有一個質疑的，只是看影片的在質疑」。而「詠春點穴大師」呂剛則表示「應該是真的」，他解釋「點穴其實分為點穴和打穴，嚴格來說霍燕山這個不叫點穴，而是打穴。」呂剛指，如今能夠練成「點穴」的人極少，「現在更多的是打穴。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1035556-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%95%A3%E6%89%93%E5%86%A0%E8%BB%8D%E8%A2%AB%E3%80%8C%E9%BB%9E%E7%A9%B4%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%AB%E3%80%8DK.O++%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD%E9%80%A0%E5%81%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1035556-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%2595%25A3%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%25BB%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%25BB%259E%25E7%25A9%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E3%2580%258DK.O%2B%2B%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%25AF%2594%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E9%2580%25A0%25E5%2581%2587&d=ItsvLBlInL5d1alZeSWtsCq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=f0f71984\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1035556-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%2595%25A3%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%25BB%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%25BB%259E%25E7%25A9%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E3%2580%258DK.O%2B%2B%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%25AF%2594%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E9%2580%25A0%25E5%2581%2587&h=4fa4078a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1035556-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%95%A3%E6%89%93%E5%86%A0%E8%BB%8D%E8%A2%AB%E3%80%8C%E9%BB%9E%E7%A9%B4%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%AB%E3%80%8DK.O++%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD%E9%80%A0%E5%81%87</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ITmXzfaVjXs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DITmXzfaVjXs&d=ItsvLBlInL5d1alZeSWtsCq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=fb3411db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ITmXzfaVjXs</a>"},{"pid":"2ca2039bf6c85032c07a1e7d71077e2bff5224fc","tid":1280500,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:04:01.000Z","msg":"俾個水印遮左睇乜"},{"pid":"b10fe32e2c23d19f9c52d224f4500af8f0504d70","tid":1280500,"uid":9722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:05:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3091aef4b09f2e5fea0076b04be6b22d176c5f75","tid":1280500,"uid":51436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:15:01.000Z","msg":"留名睇狂人挑戰點穴大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2252ab704baaedf1d6742428d34327ec8afb7f","tid":1280500,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:16:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b04b2d644bf58dd57a26125bfc36bac7b0d88654","tid":1280500,"uid":65530,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:16:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ffd9e08b6208b4f8510881bcf94dc839d6eb769","tid":1280500,"uid":103230,"like":0,"di